org.apache.derby.mbeans

Interface JDBCMBean 


  •        public interface
       
        JDBCMBean
    Management and information for the embedded JDBC driver.

    Key properties for registered MBean:

    • type=JDBC
    • system= runtime system identifier (see overview)
